{
  "stem": "6773.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We shouldn't break out or so, whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When they were shooting at the train, they killed the four-- the four SS men, including maybe 30 Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I caught two bullets-- one bullet in my leg and one bullet in my back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was taken off in North Hausen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So they, they, they took me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They threw me down from the-- from the-- from the truck, and they took me to the [INAUDIBLE] Hospital.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They needed the workers at that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They couldn't leave you to die in there out on the field.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After they shot-- they shot us, everybody who was alive, was able to run, jumped down from the-- from the train and was running out to the field.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I could only run a short period of time, and then I had to sit down, because I couldn't-- I was shot in my-- in my leg and my back.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I remained there until they picked me up, and they put me on the truck with all the dead people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was on top.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they took me to the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I came-- when we came into the camp, they took me off from the top.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They took me to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I remained at-- there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The first three weeks, I had a bullet in my leg and they didn't even know that I have a bullet in my leg.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And from the bullet I got a gangrene.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So in about, about three weeks later on, there came in a doctor, a Polish doctor from our city.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was just plain luck.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Dr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Pollock.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He came in and they took me in to see what happening with my leg.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
